# NexusCore LLM Routing Rules

## 1. モデル分類
Primary:
- glm-4-plus (GLM via Zhipu AI)
- glm-5.1 (GLM via Zhipu AI)

Secondary:
- minimax-m2.7 (MiniMax)

Lightweight:
- glm-4-flash (GLM via Zhipu AI)

## 2. プロファイルマッピング
code_generate:
  - primary: glm_codex (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

test_generate:
  - primary: glm_codex (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

code_review:
  - primary: glm_strict (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

debug:
  - primary: glm_codex (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

self_heal:
  - primary: glm_codex (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

architect:
  - primary: glm_strict (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

plan_generate:
  - primary: minimax_analytical
  - secondary: glm_strict
  - fallback: glm_default

requirement:
  - primary: glm_strict (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_analytical
  - fallback: glm_default

general:
  - primary: glm_default (glm-4-plus)
  - secondary: minimax_default
  - fallback: glm_nano

routing_classify:
  - primary: glm_nano (glm-4-flash)
  - secondary: glm_default
  - fallback: glm_nano

## 3. 環境変数
- GLM_API_KEY: Zhipu AI API key
- GLM_API_BASE: GLM base URL (default: https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4)
- GLM_MODEL: Model override (default: glm-4-plus)
- MINIMAX_API_KEY: MiniMax API key
- MINIMAX_API_BASE: MiniMax base URL (default: https://api.minimax.chat/v1)
- MINIMAX_MODEL: Model override (default: minimax-m2.7)

## 4. Consensus Algorithm
- signature: normalized hash
- weight: model trust score
- vote: weighted majority
- fallback: primary model output
